btn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() enabled=not enabled btn.Text=enabled and "ON" or "OFF" btn.BackgroundColor3=enabled and Color3.fromRGB(60,160,115) or Color3.fromRGB(80,80,90) btn.TextColor3=enabled and Color3.new(0,0,0) or Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255) status.Text=enabled and "Active" or "Paused" status.TextColor3=enabled and Color3.fromRGB(167,139,250) or Color3.fromRGB(150,150,150) end)

-- Main loop
task.spawn(function()
    while true do
        if enabled and #cache>0 then
            local target=cache[1] if target then
                local hrp=getHRP() local part=getAdornee(target)
                local dist=hrp and part and (hrp.Position-part.Position).Magnitude or math.huge
                if dist>TP_RANGE then status.Text="Teleporting..." teleport(target) task.wait(0.5) end
                hrp,part=getHRP(),getAdornee(target) dist=hrp and part and (hrp.Position-part.Position).Magnitude or math.huge
                if dist<=STEAL_RADIUS then
                    local p=getPrompt(target) if p then
                        status.Text="Stealing "..(target.name or "?").."..." steal(p) status.Text="Active"
                    end
                else status.Text="Moving..." end
            end
        else status.Text=enabled and "Scanning..." or "Paused" end
        task.wait(0.3)
    end
end)

